ar Mokhtarifar|Mokhtarifar]]}}<br>{{nowrap|{{pengoal}} [[Hamid Derakhshan|Derakhshan]]}}<br>{{nowrap|{{pengoal}} [[Reza Ahadi|Ahadi]]}}\n|align=left| [[Behrouz Soltani|Soltani]]\n| {{Hs|3}} [[1984 AFC Asian Cup#Third place play-off|Third place play-off]]\n| {{dts|format=dmy|1984-12-16}}\n|-\n| {{nts|5}}.\n| {{fb|IRN}}\n|align=center| [[1988 AFC Asian Cup#Third place play-off|0\u20130]]<sup>[[#1|1]]</sup>\n| {{fb|CHN}}\n| {{CNone|'''3\u20130'''}}\n|align=center| 0\u20133\n|align=center| 3\u20133\n|align=right| [[Ahmad Reza Abedzadeh|Abedzadeh]]\n|align=right style=\"border-bottom:3px solid gray; vertical-align:top\"| {{nowrap|[[Mojtaba Moharrami|Moharrami]] {{pengoal}}}}<br>{{nowrap|[[Farshad Pious|Pious]] {{pengoal}}}}<br>{{nowrap|{{font color||gold|[[Sirous Ghayeghran|Ghayeghran]] {{pengoal}}}}}}\n|align=left style=\"border-bottom:3px solid gray; vertical-align:top\"| {{nowrap|{{font color||#C3C3C3|{{penmiss}} [[Duan Ju]]}}}}<br>{{nowrap|{{penmiss}} [[Wang Baoshan]]}}<br>{{nowrap|{{penmiss}} [[Wu Wenbing]]}}\n|align=left| [[Zhang Huikang]]\n|rowspan=2| [[1988 AFC Asian Cup|1988, Qatar]]\n| {{Hs|5}} [[1988 AFC Asian Cup#Third place play-off|Third place play-off]]\n| {{dts|format=dmy|1988-12-17}}\n|-\n| {{nts|6}}.\n| {{fb|KSA}}\n|align=center| [[1988 AFC Asian Cup#Final|0\u20130]]\n| {{fb|KOR|1984}}\n| {{CNone|'''4\u20133'''}}\n|align=center| 1\u20132\n|align=center| 5\u20135\n|align=right| [[Abdullah Al-Deayea|A. Al-Deayea]]\n|align=right style=\"border-bottom:3px solid gray; vertical-align:top\"| {{nowrap|[[Saleh Nu'eimeh|Nu'eimehl]] {{pengoal}}}}<br>{{nowrap|[[Mohamed Abd Al-Jawad|Abd Al-Jawad]] {{penmiss}}}}<br>{{nowrap|[[Majed Abdullah|M. Abdullah]] {{pengoal}}}}<br>{{nowrap|[[Saleh Al-Mutlaq|Al-Mutlaq]] {{pengoal}}}}<br>{{nowrap|{{font color||gold|[[Fahad Al-Bishi|Al-Bishi]] {{pengoal}}}}}}\n|align=left style=\"border-bottom:3px solid gray; vertical-align:top\"| {{nowrap|{{font color||#C3C3C3|{{penmiss}} [[Cho Min-Kook]]}}}}<br>{{nowrap|{{pengoal}} [[Lee Tae-Ho