a Golmohammadi|Golmohammadi]]}}}}\n|align=left| [[Ebrahim Mirzapour|Mirzapour]]\n|{{Hs|5}} [[2004 AFC Asian Cup#Semifinals|Semi-finals]]\n| {{dts|format=dmy|2004-08-03}}\n|-\n| {{nts|14}}.\n| {{fb|JPN}}\n|align=center| [[2007 AFC Asian Cup knockout stage#Japan vs Australia|1\u20131]]\n| {{fb|AUS}}\n| {{CNone|'''4\u20133'''}}\n|align=center| 1\u20132\n|align=center| 5\u20135\n|align=right| [[Yoshikatsu Kawaguchi|Kawaguchi]]\n|align=right style=\"border-bottom:3px solid gray; vertical-align:top\"| {{nowrap|[[Shunsuke Nakamura|S. Nakamura]] {{pengoal}}}} <br>{{nowrap|[[Yasuhito End\u014d|End\u014d]]}} {{pengoal}}<br>{{nowrap|[[Y\u016bichi Komano|Komano]]}} {{pengoal}}<br>{{nowrap|[[Naohiro Takahara|Takahara]]}} {{penmiss}}<br>{{nowrap|{{font color||gold|[[Yuji Nakazawa|Nakazawa]] {{pengoal}} }}}}\n|align=left style=\"border-bottom:3px solid gray; vertical-align:top\"| {{nowrap|{{penmiss}} {{font color||#C3C3C3|[[Harry Kewell|Kewell]]}}}}<br>{{penmiss}} {{nowrap|[[Lucas Neill|Neill]]}}<br>{{pengoal}} {{nowrap|[[Tim Cahill|Cahill]]}}<br>{{pengoal}} {{nowrap|[[Nick Carle|Carle]]}}<br>{{pengoal}} {{nowrap|[[David Carney|Carney]]}} \n|align=left| [[Mark Schwarzer|Schwarzer]]\n|rowspan=4| [[2007 AFC Asian Cup|2007, Vietnam/Malaysia/Thailand/Indonesia]]\n|rowspan=2| {{Hs|4}} [[2004 AFC Asian Cup#Quarter-finals|Quarter-finals]]\n| {{dts|format=dmy|2007-07-21}}\n|-\n| {{nts|15}}.\n| {{fb|KOR|1997}}\n|align=center| [[2007 AFC Asian Cup knockout stage#Iran vs South Korea|0\u20130]]\n| {{fb|IRN}}\n| {{CNone|'''4\u20132'''}}\n|align=center| 1\u20132\n|align=center| 5\u20134\n|align=right| [[Lee Woon-Jae]]\n|align=right style=\"border-bottom:3px solid gray; vertical-align:top\"| {{nowrap|{{font color||#C3C3C3|[[Lee Chun-soo]] {{pengoal}}}}}}<br>{{nowrap|[[Kim Sang-sik]] {{penmiss}}}}<br>{{nowrap|[[Kim Do-heon]] {{pengoal}}}}<br>{{nowrap|[[Cho Jae-jin]] {{pengoal}}}}<br>{{nowrap|{{font color||gold|[[Kim Jung-woo]] {{pengoal}}}}}}\n|align=left style=\"border-bottom:3px solid gray; ver